            </div>
            
            <div class="double-moral">
                <strong>THE CYNICAL TECH MORAL:</strong> In software, every "bug" is just an undocumented feature‚Äîuntil it eats your production database. Also, alert fatigue is real. Don't cry wolf, don't cry bug, and for the love of all that's holy, ADD PROPER LOGGING!
            </div>

